{"tid":345231,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"蘋果指名要靠騰訊","createTime":"2017-08-03T00:55:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-03T10:26:19.000Z","uid":104804,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3f3fac84c07e593344d24ad4d3bf8986bf38fac1","tid":345231,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T00:55:56.000Z","msg":"今日仲唔爆升<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n【香港市場不振拖累大中華表現】<br />\n【蘋果：期望與騰訊有更多合作】<br />\n<br />\niPhone 面世接近十年，累積賣出超過 12 億部。<br />\n<br />\niPhone 手機、平板電腦 iPad ，兩大主打產品，帶動蘋果公司上季賺超過 87 億美元，收入超過 454 億美元，盈利和收入都比市場預期理想。<br />\n<br />\n蘋果公司預期，今季收入介乎 490 至 520 億美元。<br />\n<br />\n分析相信是暗示，新一代 iPhone 會在 9 月左右推出，帶動今季銷售強勁。<br />\n<br />\n不過包括中、港、台三地的大中華市場，按季急跌兩成半。<br />\n<br />\n行政總裁庫克表示，大中華地區表現，受香港市場不振拖累。<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;Hong Kong continued to drag down the total greater China segment&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n又點名指，騰訊微信用戶群大，有助擴展 iOS 在內地市佔率，期望與騰訊有更多合作。<br />\n<br />\n#有線新聞　#蘋果　#業績　#盈利　#香港市場　#不振　#拖累"},{"pid":"d55b57a60efab05f94b1a94149bebb2c62661499","tid":345231,"uid":29197,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T00:56:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c0dd9f61540a53e0bf426b1c13d6c6db02f00b7","tid":345231,"uid":30604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T00:58:06.000Z","msg":"Apple + Tencent <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c18f53c49e77af5f420f87fa2f91b5604c5b46c","tid":345231,"uid":102132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T00:59:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"eb691573b9c472620a6a14a41ca066e8f5fa8575","tid":345231,"uid":33907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T01:02:29.000Z","msg":"食屎啦 香港拖支那？死基佬落地獄啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clo